{"tid":6302,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東京五日四夜","createTime":"2016-11-27T09:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T15:50:28.000Z","uid":18214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21b66fbda5cc07e9b902c72d24549ca312b1d68a","tid":6302,"uid":18214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:43:52.000Z","msg":"黎緊一月去東京<br />\nplan 緊去輕井澤，富士急，迪士尼海洋，橫濱呢d 地方<br />\n煩緊住宿應該住新宿，東京站附近定係其他地方<br />\n各位巴絲可唔可以俾d 意見我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d0bcfe3cf5083d2ab8fb93cfd7c2e03c2cc8f5","tid":6302,"uid":16902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:18:18.000Z","msg":"巴打去輕井澤 係滑雪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我1月都東京 諗緊去唔去井澤好<br />\n同埋個邊有咩好食推介<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得新宿都ok <br />\n其實只要環繞東京嗰條線事旦一個站都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7be4aeaa74abe5f70db114e9938015b8ead737","tid":6302,"uid":18214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:49:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a03238c1c2f75c6b556830fbe6bdb1ae8dbd51b","tid":6302,"uid":30996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:16:10.000Z","msg":"黎緊一月中去東京 都係想輕井澤滑雪"},{"pid":"6ce471dc11e6eb09c055089d2846529d11fc3249","tid":6302,"uid":2998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:35:25.000Z","msg":"日日都去大外檔，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e5357c5a9a1962ff4327c4fee48b4c3233bf4e","tid":6302,"uid":5309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:40:43.000Z","msg":"我都係一月去 去八日<br />\n頭一日去河口湖浸溫泉 其餘未plan"},{"pid":"953fed4a2b45e6278d2df75fa9fd600d752e4991","tid":6302,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB